      <title>挪威邮轮公司股价下跌，因盈利前景提高未能给人留下深刻印象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/norwegian-cruise-falls-as-raised-profit-outlook-fails-to-impress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威邮轮控股有限公司(Norwegian Cruise Line Holdings Ltd.)因盈利前景改善而令投资者在行业繁荣导致航行需求创纪录之际的高预期落空，股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/norwegian-cruise-falls-as-raised-profit-outlook-fails-to-impress</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
